us now is on aligning the selected foods with the planned days, to ensure that each day is nutritionally balanced. I'm meticulously confirming all entries for accuracy. I'm paying close attention to the details of the products so that the meals align with the plans exactly.\n\n\n**Confirming Food Attributes**\n\nI'm now confirming the IDs, PLUs, and categories of menu items to ensure precise integration into the meal plan. Specifically, I've checked and verified the following: Hummus (ID: 849, PLU: 4183545, Cat: Закуски), Niçoise Salad (ID: 679, PLU: 4398544, Cat: Салаты), Pumpkin Soup (ID: 835, PLU: 4273862, Cat: Первые блюда), Turkey Cutlets with Buckwheat (ID: 712, PLU: 4422205, Cat: Основные блюда), Beetroot Salad with Pesto (ID: 687, PLU: 4331972, Cat: Салаты), and Vegetable Stew (ID: 726, PLU: 4445758, Cat: Основные блюда). I'm focusing on the matching the main entries exactly.\n\n\n**Validating Item IDs**\n\nI'm now integrating more menu item details by validating IDs, PLUs, and categories to ensure accurate meal plan entries. I am confirming the selections: 60г (ID: 724, PLU: 4421287, Cat: Основные блюда), Borscht with Beef (ID: 837, PLU: 4437971, Cat: Первые блюда), Tortiglioni with Turkey (ID: 731, PLU: 4409319, Cat: Основные блюда), Vegetable Vinaigrette (ID: 706, PLU: 3681084, Cat: Салаты), BBQ Turkey Salad (ID: 681, PLU: 4147826, Cat: Салаты), Chicken Meatball Soup (ID: 836, PLU: 4438649, Cat: Первые блюда), Wok with Beef (ID: 751, PLU: 4175863, Cat: Основные блюда) and Cucumber Mini-Roll (ID: 790, PLU: 4467008, Cat: Закуски). I am now verifying all details.\n\n\n**Verifying Remaining Menu Items**\n\nI'm now integrating the final selections into the meal plan, carefully reviewing each item. I've validated: Chicken Fillet with Mushrooms and Potatoes (ID: 728, PLU: 4389855, Cat: Основные блюда), Mushroom Cream Soup (ID: 830, PLU: 4324261, Cat: Первые блюда), Chicken Wok (ID: 730, PLU: 4175864, Cat: Основные блюда), Lenten Coleslaw (ID: 677, PLU: 4396281, 